       <span class="docSource"><span class="dType"><abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ recipients copy (A recipients copy is assumed to be in the hand of the signer unless it is otherwise described.) ]">RC</abbr></span> (<span class="ref-terms">Adams Papers</span>).</span>
      </p>

     </div>
     <div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA06d096n1-ptr" id="PJA06d096n1">1</a>
      
   <p>A reference to the letter from the Committee for Foreign Affairs of <a href="default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-06-06-02-0087" class="document">14 May</a> (below), but see <a href="default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-06-06-02-0087&amp;expandNote=PJA06d102n4#PJA06d102n4" class="document">note 4</a> there for an additional letter from the Committee of <a href="default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-06-08-03-0001-0110" class="document">15 May</a> (not printed here).</p>

     </div>
     <div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA06d096n2-ptr" id="PJA06d096n2">2</a>
      
   <p>See the Commerce Committee to the Commissioners, <a href="default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-06-06-02-0094" class="document">16 May</a> (below).</p>

